snippet: Nationals shortstop Ian Desmond made two errors that helped the Reds get back in the game, but he hit a home run in the 11th inning to help rally Washington.
abstract: MLB Roundup; Washington Nationals rally in the 11th inning to earn a 7-6 victory over Cincinnati Reds; other baseball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Nationals shortstop Ian Desmond made two errors that helped the Reds get back in the game, but he hit a home run in the 11th inning to help rally Washington.

headline.seo: Washington Nationals Blow a Lead But Still Beat Reds
headline.main: Nationals Blow Lead but Prevail in the 11th
